Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer for lease, 347 Lytton Road, Morningside. Morningside is one of the most tightly held industrial suburbs and offers easy access to the Port of Brisbane, Brisbane CBD and the major arterial networks servicing South-East Queensland. 

Some of the following leasing attributes are: 

+ Total building area of 13,317sqm* combining cold/dry storage & office accommodation
+ Site area of 40,720sqm* providing two street access
+ Ample hardstand for easy truck access, container storage and onsite car parking
+ Highly competitive rental rates & flexible leasing terms on offer
+ Areas from 2,000sqm* –13,317sqm*available to lease (available from 1st July 2020)
+ Ability to lease spaces separately, such as office accommodation and dry/cold storage
+ Pre lease options available from 5,000 – 20,0000sqm (request further information)

*Approx. 

For further information regarding leasing opportunities or should you wish to arrange an inspection, please contact Exclusive Marketing Agents, Peter Turnbull or Ben Lyons of CBRE.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: MORNINGSIDE COLD STORAGE – VALUE FOR MONEY & LEASING FLEXIBILITY ON OFFER!

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
360 Lytton Road is strategically located within the heart of Morningside, situated on main Lytton Road offering excellent connectivity to the CBD, Airport, Port and major transport routes North & South. Morningside is regarded as one of Brisbane’s blue chip industrial suburbs and is surrounded by excellent amenity.

There are two tenancies on offer at 360 Lytton Road, Morningside. Some of the features of each opportunity include:

Building 1:

•	986sqm* corporate office accommodation split over two floors
•	Full kitchen and amenities on both levels 
•	Fully fitted out with multiple offices, boardrooms & open plan areas
•	Opportunity to split into two tenancies
•	Excellent natural light throughout
•	Huge exposure to main Lytton road with excellent signage opportunity
•	Dedicated on-site exclusive car parks which are fully fenced and secure
•	Available from October/November 2020

Building 4:

•	1,333sqm* highbay warehouse accessed via two electric container height roller doors
•	Massive internal clearance of approx. 10m*
•	Accessed via 2 x electric container height roller doors
•	Designed to be split into two smaller tenancies
•	Situated within a secure and gated complex
•	Opportunity to build office space to suit
*Approx.

For further information regarding these two tenancies on offer or to arrange your inspection, please contact Exclusive Agent Ben Lyons of CBRE.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: LOOKING FOR YOUR NEXT CORPORATE OFFICE HQ OR WAREHOUSING FACILITY?

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are excited to present to the market exclusively, the latest stage of Rivermakers, Brisbane -  ‘The Depot’. This exciting opportunity is situated within the  heart of the Morningside-Colmslie precinct offering huge exposure to main Lytton & Junction Road’s. 

Located within the Australia Tradecoast precinct, Morningside remains one of the most highly sought after hubs and has transformed significantly over the last 5 years. Morningside is a precinct which will continue to grow and evolve in the future and presents ample opportunities for many users long term.

The Depot’s location provides excellent access to major arterial road networks including Lytton Road which connects directly to the Gateway Motorway, one of Queensland most significant corridors connecting the Gold and Sunshine Coasts.

Some of the salient features of the soon to be completed Rivermakers – The Depot include:

-	Large 11,000sqm* trade centre currently under construction - estimated completion March 2020.
-	Up to 3,000sqm available for lease in one line with flexible tenancy sizing.
-	Traditional on grade design with rear loading capabilities
-	Excellent internal height and natural light throughout
-	Easy access to the centre with multi directional off Lytton Road and Colmslie Road
-	Close to some of Brisbane’s most affluent suburbs like Bulimba, Balmoral, Hawthorne and Morningside.
-	5 minutes from Bulimba Barracks (largest inner city redevelopment in a decade)
-	Local population forecast to reach 200,000+ people by 2026.
-	1km to Cannon Hill train station
-	Centralised location 10km from Brisbane CBD, 10km from Brisbane Airport, 3km from Cannon Hill & 2km from Gateway Motorway
-	Average household income for local area is $96,000, 12% higher than Brisbane average. 
-	Area spend 10% higher than the Brisbane average. 
-	Outstanding signage and branding opportunities onto busy Lytton Road
-	Located next to the Lytton, Junction & Colmslie Road round-a-bout with 36,000+ passing vehicles daily.’
-	Versatile landlord that will work with all tenants to handover a suitable tenancy.

For further information https://rivermakers.com.au/

For further information on Rivermakers The Depot, please contact exclusive agents Sam Macgregor or Ben Lyons of CBRE.

We look forward to discussing this outstanding opportunity with you further.

STCA
